- [stress-ng](https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/stress-test-linux-unix-server-with-stress-ng/)

# memory stress test
sudo stress-ng --vm 2 --vm-bytes 12G --timeout 60s --metrics-brief

# cpu stress test
sudo stress-ng --cpu 4 --timeout 60s --metrics-brief

# disk stress test
sudo stress-ng --disk 2 --io 2 --timeout 60s --metrics-brief
